				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-xu%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99ng-qu%C3%A1n/poem-0qg0wLLBVz8hcI6tMlgMSQ">Đặng xuân mộng quán - 鄧春夢館</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/%C4%90%E1%BA%BF-kinh-thi%C3%AAn/poem-9NRXjE-zAkH_P0dE0rQmRA">Đế kinh thiên - 帝京篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-jvbfrjspi2Y6S8b3jeqzpA">Lạc Tân Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-qu%E1%BB%91c-c%C3%B4ng/poem-INY17-RNUcI9Mon73JkysQ">Nguyễn quốc công - 阮國公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-0a-SzHNUsJjP7BQud8rJYw">Bùi Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/S%C6%A1-h%E1%BA%A1-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-vvCMv8z_hBcGIPDNCpqFXg">Sơ hạ tức sự - 初夏即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-9cGSHCUvFAIW_3kTfbKANw">Vương An Thạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tam-Xuy%C3%AAn-quan-thu%E1%BB%B7-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-dYBU0BMWy96tMiL8Yl7EFA">Tam Xuyên quan thuỷ trướng nhị thập vận - 三川觀水漲二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%B7ng-n%E1%BB%99i-I/poem-UL7Xr5cf7JCmvHBE7R8uHA">Tặng nội (I) - 贈內（I）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Duy-Thi%E1%BB%87n/T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-iHRAqdXO-wy07FS6APKAQA">Tây Hồ trúc chi từ kỳ 2 - 西湖竹枝詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Duy-Thi%E1%BB%87n/author-0WlAguiyNNcFbVPXWu6PqA">Tiền Duy Thiện</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%C6%B0ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%ADp-Th%E1%BB%A5c/poem-el3KcYxCmG2yCsj_ulIoZA">Tống khách nhập Thục - 送客入蜀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%C6%B0ng/author-QFMuZjhV-exDsfukXJ1w3Q">Dương Ngưng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/T%E1%BB%91ng-ti%E1%BB%81n-v%E1%BB%87-huy%E1%BB%87n-L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%A9m-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7/poem--n16aGXVq7-dtrrOjuRf2g">Tống tiền vệ huyện Lý Thẩm thiếu phủ - 送前衛縣李寀少府</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/author-daTT9TQ-QJ39piO86WPo5Q">Cao Thích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A0nh/T%E1%BB%A9-s%E1%BA%A7u-thi/poem-DU-Xoj-ZhfCDiwOq0PYG-A">Tứ sầu thi - 四愁詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A0nh/author-L37GQHbELmLdeisdE7nPzQ">Trương Hành</a>)<br></div>	</div>
